heir minds.- The withdrawal period will start from the moment the consumer receives the goods, rather than when the contract is concluded, which was the case before. The rules apply to internet, phone and mail order sales, as well as to sales outside shops, for example on the consumer's doorstep, in the street, at a party at home or during an excursion organised by the trader"
